# Tsumi TV — environment variables.
#
# NONE are required for browsing/streaming: AniList needs no key, and each user
# supplies their own Real-Debrid key on the TV itself. The Supabase pair below is
# only needed to enable phone PAIRING (Settings → Pair with phone). Without them,
# pairing shows a graceful "not set up" message and everything else still works.
#
# Use the SAME values as your main Tsumi site's Vercel project.

# Enables device pairing (tv/supabase/tv_devices.sql must be run once).
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
